    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(…) Secunda <rs>carta</rs> continebat quomodo <persName>Anso</persName> et
                            <persName>Aliprando</persName> [ger]mani, filii
                            <persName>Ansprandi</persName> vendiderunt eidem domno
                            <persName>Arigis</persName> casalem suum in loco
                            <placeName>Lucerola</placeName>, id est [ip]sa vinea, terra uno
                        teniente, <rs>coniuncta</rs> de uno latere cum terra ecclesie
                            <orgName>Sancti Stephani</orgName>, [et] alie finis sicut in ipsa carta
                        legitur; scripta per <persName><persName>Benenatum</persName></persName>
                        <rs>notarium</rs> in anno tertio decimo gloriosi duc[i]s domni Arigis gentis
                        Langobardorum. </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
